creator: Bart Bonte
descriptionHtml:
'Boo!' is a spooky puzzle game for you!

To solve the puzzles you have to dip the pumpkin in different paints and wear attributes to mask certain parts of the pumpkin.
The puzzles starts easy but it gets more difficult!

21 Halloween themed levels, based on my premium app 'Factory Balls'.

Happy Halloween and have fun,
@BartBonte

descriptionHtml:
'Boo!' is a spooky puzzle game for you!

To solve the puzzles you have to dip the pumpkin in the different paints and wear attributes to mask certain parts of the pumpkin.
The puzzles start easy but it gets more difficult!
Can you make the correct pumpkin in 42 Halloween themed levels?
Complete all the levels to unlock the brand new daily puzzle mode.

Happy Halloween,
@BartBonte

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What's new?
- The number of levels has doubled, there are now 42 levels!
- There's a new attribute appearing from level 22 on!
- Complete all the levels and unlock the brand new daily puzzle mode!
Happy Halloween!
